WEBVTT

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:33.576
(Laughter)

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:35.736
It was the craziest thing, guys,

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:39.096
but when it came to my influence
and my exposure,

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:41.360
I literally took a quantum leap.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.056
So I made more videos

00:00:44.080 --> 00:00:46.496
and the subject matter of my videos

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:50.856
was often the most divisive subject
in American life,

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:53.416
but it was the way that I articulated race

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.800
that made me somewhat
of a digital lightning rod.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:59.576
See, being a survivor myself
of police brutality

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:01.896
and having lost a childhood friend,